publisher			Michael Brough							
publish_time	 2011年6月10日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Vertex Dispenser is an abstract real-time strategy game with mathematical puzzle elements. Move around a geometric surface and lay claim to your territory. Protect it by capturing solid faces for defense. Manipulate the colours of your vertices to gain power for special abilities. Balance your time between attacking, defending, expanding and colouring to survive and defeat your enemies.							Key Features:							Single-player campaign mode							Single-player puzzle mode							Team-based multi-player							Cross-platform multi-player - Play with both your PC and Mac friends													
